snippet.title: Black Clover: Quartet Knights - Announcement Trailer | PS4, PC
snippet.description:
In a world where magic is commonplace, knights will stand up to decide who is the "Ultimate Knight"!  Jump in for some epic 4 vs 4 and third person shooter action when Black Clover: Quartet Knights arrives for the PS4 and PC in 2018.
